Initialization for the API instance. An init method method must be called prior to other methods in this class. The OSN server URL will be retrieved from Topology Manager (OSN module) and the login credentials will be looked up by the OSN connection manager API. This method uses the OSN ConnectionManager API to setup the connection to the OSN instance.
